::Kluster/Shredder::

Kluster walks into the landing bay, seeing Phobia already there. He looks 
from Phobia's ship to Phobia. He then looks at the crates.

"We'll take them to cargo hold one," he says, pointing to a door, "Right 
behind that door. Hysteria will check them over there."

Kluster walks over to one of the crates, ready to lift it along with Phobia.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Shredder raises an eyebrow as Magmatron adresses what was seemingly a wall as 
'Phobia'. He frowns. Was his leader insane? Maybe the presence of Unicron had 
driven him to that condition....

He looks at Magmatron when the bot aproaches him again. "So what are we doing 
now?"
